
### 必要なもの

#### postcss-cli

```sample.sh

	# https://github.com/postcss/postcss-cli
	yarn add --dev postcss-cli

	# sample
	postcss --no-map --use postcss-nested -o ./path/to/dist.css ./path/to/src.css

```

